##### screen brightness #####
XF86MonBrightnessDown
  sudo brightnessctl set 20%-

XF86MonBrightnessUp
  sudo brightnessctl set 20%+

##### Volume #####
XF86Audio{Raise,Lower}Volume
  ~/bin/volume {+,-}10%
XF86AudioMute
  ~/bin/volume-toggle-mute
XF86AudioMicMute
  ~/bin/microphone-toggle
